==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wideness
<hw>Wide"ness</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
quality or state of being wide; breadth; width; great extent from side
to side; <as>as, the <ex>wideness</ex> of a room</as>.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧I
landed in a small creek about the <xex>wideness</xex> of my
canoe.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Large extent in all directions; broadness;
greatness; <as>as, the <ex>wideness</ex> of the sea or
ocean</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Widespread</ent>⟦br⟧
